EqualSamplingEffortDetail: Sampling included a defined number of kicks, jabs, or approximate areas in a series of similar habitats among all streams, followed by a 15-minute timed visual search/handpick with 2 persons. These multi-habitat subsamples were then combined into a single sample for the site. Specifically for this site: Riffle (3 kicks in main channel, two 1/2 sq m snags on channel margin), Run (1 kick in main channel 1 sq m vegetation in channel margin, 1 sq m in macrophyte bed in channel margin, 1/2 sq m woody snag, 1 kick in bar in main channel, 1 leaf pack), and Pool (1 kick in main channel pool), plus 15 minute visual search with two persons.
MultihabitatSamplingEffort: Sampling included a defined number of kicks, jabs, or approximate areas in a series of similar habitats among all streams, followed by a 15-minute timed visual search/handpick with 2 persons. These multi-habitat subsamples were then combined into a single sample for the site. Specifically for this site: Riffle (3 kicks in main channel, two 1/2 sq m snags on channel margin), Run (1 kick in main channel 1 sq m vegetation in channel margin, 1 sq m in macrophyte bed in channel margin, 1/2 sq m woody snag, 1 kick in bar in main channel, 1 leaf pack), and Pool (1 kick in main channel pool), plus 15 minute visual search with two persons.
